@node REQR "System Requirements"

@{FG Highlight}System Requirements@{FG Text}
@{code}
To use PageStream 3.0, BME 2.0 and PageLiner 2.0, you must have at least:

Computer:  any Amiga model.

Memory:    3MB total RAM (at least 512K chip RAM),
           4MB RAM or more is highly recommended.

Drives:    hard drive with 3.6 to 12.4MB free space.

Workbench: AmigaDOS 2.04 or higher.

Printer (optional):
- Epson dot matrix/ink jet or compatible;
- Hewlett Packard DeskJet or compatible;
- Hewlett Packard LaserJet or compatible;
- Fargo Primera;
- PostScript laser printer, imagesetter or device;
- or any Preferences compatible printer.
@{body}
@{body}
@toc PageStream3:Help/PGS.HEL/MAIN
@endnode

